---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Privacy Policy | Kanon',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-6 py-24 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-slate-300">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-slate-500">Last Updated: February 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        At Kanon, we are committed to protecting the privacy of our users and the security of the healthcare data managed through our platform. This policy outlines how we handle information.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">1. Data Security & HIPAA</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Kanon is designed with privacy-first principles. We understand the sensitive nature of Home Health data. Any data collected is encrypted in transit and at rest, and we maintain administrative, physical, and technical safeguards designed to support HIPAA compliance.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        For our early access waitlist, we collect basic contact information (Name, Email, Agency Name, Role). This information is used solely to communicate regarding Kanon’s development and alpha access.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">3. No Sale of Data</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information or your agency's data to third parties. We are a workflow tool, not a data brokerage.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">4. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        If you have questions about our privacy practices, please contact us at 
        <a 
            href="mailto:privacy&#64;kanoncare&#46;health?subject=Privacy&#32;Inquiry" 
            class="text-cyan-500 hover:text-cyan-400 underline decoration-cyan-500/30 underline-offset-4 transition-colors"
        >
            privacy&#64;kanoncare&#46;health
        </a>.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800">
      <a href="/" class="text-cyan-500 hover:text-cyan-400 font-medium">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>